channel.title: [HELP] MoparScape not working? [HELP]
channel.description:
I have been using moparscape on my other computer, my mom took it away. So now i use my old laptop and downloaded moparscape. When i tried to run the bat it had the downloading cache thing. it kept stopping at 10% then went to requesting title screen then it failed there "retry in 10 seconds" .... "retry in 50 secs"
so then i said f that... the cache is going to take 2 long to dl so i went to windows folder to the rs cache (.file_store_32) and copied all the files to the .mpr_file_store_32
then now i tried to run the moparscape bat when it was going to load up
IT GOES
"STARTING UP"
sorry an error has occured whils loading runescape then a whole bunch of bs wannabe help tips
is it okay to just use the runescape cache in .file_store_32 for the .mpr_file_store_32 or does moparscape have different cache?
